    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您有兴趣，请务必将游戏加入愿望清单 - 这会很有帮助！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/a77955516e636f409752bad663c853c5.avif?t=1754482218\" width=617 height=70 /></span><i>Infinitevania</i> 是一款2D平台游戏，采用类银河战士恶魔城风格，深受 <i>恶魔城：月下夜想曲</i> 的启发，并融入了 <i>空洞骑士</i> 的元素。游戏专注于战斗、探索、解谜、升级和扣人心弦的故事情节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索不同的世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败这些世界中最强大的生物，吸收它们的力量，变得更强，最终摧毁 <i>Infinitevania</i> 的核心，回到自己的世界。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/23d3ab332f71fe83c19b3c3d65cd90e4.poster.avif?t=1754482218\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/23d3ab332f71fe83c19b3c3d65cd90e4.webm?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/23d3ab332f71fe83c19b3c3d65cd90e4.mp4?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/c2d2d6d80936f9c306c83355ee0dac79.avif?t=1754482218\" width=617 height=70 /></span><strong>面对强大的敌人</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制定独特的策略，适应每一场战斗，并在冒险中不断前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/f489e08cf6340459bf1586bd2028dda4.poster.avif?t=1754482218\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/f489e08cf6340459bf1586bd2028dda4.webm?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/f489e08cf6340459bf1586bd2028dda4.mp4?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/c776734cb7d703679d02d43ff3a87088.poster.avif?t=1754482218\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/c776734cb7d703679d02d43ff3a87088.webm?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/c776734cb7d703679d02d43ff3a87088.mp4?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/2130466749aaad679baa5f16859daeab.avif?t=1754482218\" width=617 height=70 /></span><strong>解决谜题</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解决引人入胜的谜题，解锁新区域和隐藏的秘密。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/9be3294700f554e45bfb90829058060b.poster.avif?t=1754482218\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/9be3294700f554e45bfb90829058060b.webm?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/9be3294700f554e45bfb90829058060b.mp4?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/0622e5ab9fce6171d585b86ad4d87e22.avif?t=1754482218\" width=617 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存于致命陷阱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越充满危险的环境，每一步都将考验你的技能和反应能力。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/125a68ea3ab28bb29bb7ebd5d6408853.poster.avif?t=1754482218\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/125a68ea3ab28bb29bb7ebd5d6408853.webm?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/125a68ea3ab28bb29bb7ebd5d6408853.mp4?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/fa8a089643e81bdcca46c8225291378d.avif?t=1754482218\" width=617 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集升级以变得更强大</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险过程中不断提升你的能力和装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/2b31a6c7c245342ac044167ea164fd38.poster.avif?t=1754482218\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/2b31a6c7c245342ac044167ea164fd38.webm?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170570/extras/2b31a6c7c245342ac044167ea164fd38.mp4?t=1754482218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p